        "label": "NTR organization registration and approved access",
        "generateUrl": "https://services.parivahan.gov.in/ntr/#/user-registration",
        "setup": "Register your organization on the [National Transport Repository portal](https://services.parivahan.gov.in/ntr/#/user-registration). The portal says this option is for organizations that require portal or API-based access to transport data. During registration, select the organization type, verify your mobile number by OTP, provide organization/contact details, choose the data parameters you need, submit the required undertaking, and wait for MoRTH approval. After approval, you can sign in using your registered mobile number on the [NTR login page](https://services.parivahan.gov.in/ntr/#/Login)."
